    # player "A pleasure, [vivi.n]. We know who you are, [igaram.n] told us everything… We'd better find another place to talk..."
    player "Un placer, [vivi.n]. Sabemos quién eres, [igaram.n] nos lo contaste todo… Será mejor que busquemos otro sitio para hablar…"

# game/scripts/Events/Game/event_cactusisland_vivi.rpy:366
