    # nami "Well, it wasn't exactly easy!! You really weren't far from the end..."
    nami "¡Bueno, no fue precisamente fácil! Realmente estabas cerca del final..."

# game/scripts/Events/Game/event_cactusisland_vivi.rpy:394
